lu.uni.geko.weaver
Class AdviceEffectuationCalculator

java.lang.Object
  lu.uni.geko.weaver.AdviceEffectuationCalculator

public final class AdviceEffectuationCalculator
extends Object

A utility class for calculating all data structures needed for advice effectuation i.e. the sets of elements that have to be removed and added during weaving as well as the mapping from base elements to the advice elements that have to be merged with them.

calculateBaseElementsToRemove

private static Set<org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject> calculateBaseElementsToRemove(JoinPoint joinPoint,
                                                                                N2NMap<org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject,org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject> pc2AvN2NMap)
Calculates and returns a set containing all base elements to be removed. Let f denote the morphism from the pointcut to the base (joinPoint)
and let g denote the morphism from the pointcut to the advice (pc2AvN2NMap).
An element e of the base must be removed if and only if
- there is an element e' in the pointcut such that f(e')=e
- and there is NO element e'' in the advice such that g(e')=e''

Parameters:
joinPoint - a joinpoint
pc2AvN2NMap - the mapping from pointcut to advice elements
Returns:
all base elements to be removed during weaving

calculateBase2AvMergeBiN2NMap

private static BiN2NMap<org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject,org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject> calculateBase2AvMergeBiN2NMap(JoinPoint joinPoint,
                                                                                                                   N2NMap<org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject,org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject> pc2AvN2NMap)
Calculates and returns the bidirectional mapping from base elements to advice elements that have to be merged with them. Let f denote the morphism from the pointcut to the base (joinPoint)
and let g denote the morphism from the pointcut to the advice (pointcut2AdviceMap).
An element e of the base must be merged with an element e'' of the advice if and only if
- there is an element e' in the pointcut such that f(e')=e
- and there is an element e'' in the advice such that g(e')=e''

Parameters:
joinPoint - a join point
pc2AvN2NMap - the mapping from pointcut to advice elements
Returns:
the mapping from base elements to advice elements that have to be merged with them

calculateAvElementsToAdd

private static Set<org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject> calculateAvElementsToAdd(Advice advice,
                                                                           N2NMap<org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject,org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject> pc2AvN2NMap)
Calculates and returns a set containing all advice elements to be removed. Let g denote the morphism from the pointcut to the advice (pc2AvN2NMap).
An element e of the advice must be added to the base if and only if
- there is NO element e' in the pointcut such that g(e')=e

Parameters:
advice - an advice
pc2AvN2NMap - the mapping from pointcut to advice elements
Returns:
all advice elements to be removed
